.DT
set_price
Disk World creator help
set_price

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
set_price -  This function sets the base price for unlocking a door.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int set_price(int price)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^price%^RESET%^ - the base-price in money-units
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
1 on success, 0 on failure
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/npc/locksmith.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This function sets the base price for unlocking a door.  If the savefile is
set, a killer will be charged the double price.
.EP

